description:
@Gabriele N: The issue you reported is in my to do list.

@Derek H: For the time being, to improve smoothness, you could hide the read articles. This is in my to do list, nonetheless.
Latest update: Added basic GReader integration. 

Don't forget to rate people and send me your feedback.
*******************************************
Slide Reader is a beautiful webOS application that will make reading news a pleasure. The attractive UI makes this app a must-have. Features: dual view (you can switch between a clean text summary or go directly to the website), dashboard (continue browsing through stories while reading an article), themes (choose from different themes the one that pleases your eye), dictionary (encountered a word that you're unsure of its meaning? just go to the dictionary and look it up), stay up to date (you can configure the reader to update in the background or you can do it yourself instantly with a single tap). Coming up in future releases: Sync with Google Reader, share via Facebook, Twitter, email and Instapaper, Feed Catalog. Stay tuned and don't hesitate to contact us to let us know of what features you want implemented or what areas we should improve.
